snippet.title: Drums Rock - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Drums Rock is a VR arcade drumming game in the style of your favourite rhythm games of the past, but with demons! Check out the trailer highlighting not only the popular songs available to play, but the new ability to add in your custom tracks.
